{"tid":1166765,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HUAWEI手機多人放　回收價急跌一成！","createTime":"2019-05-22T15:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T18:27:46.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3bf56ca28badba4c2a3a6b6d1c73ad921d1b35d","tid":1166765,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190522/photo/bkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001_01p.jpg&h=91755126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHUAWEI被美國封殺，有機會對P30系列的銷情造成影響。（設計圖片）<br />\n<br />\nHUAWEI被「封殺」引起用家們極大回響，除擔心將來未能更新系統或應用程式，更擔心日後有機無人收！衛訊日前就發表聲明，指出如顧客有意換購手機，其Trade in服務將維持不變，包括所有HUAWEI手機。電訊供應商又點呢？之前被發現Trade-in欄刪去了HUAWEI的CSL，更新後該內容已「重現天日」，並列明了最新P30系列的回收價。至於中國移動香港的「舊換新」計劃則依然有HUAWEI手機在清單內，用戶們暫時可以放心。 <br />\n<br />\n然而有人收機，不代表回收價不受影響。據先達三禾電氣店長Simon哥表示，在封殺消息傳出後，截至5月21日晚為止HUAWEI手機的普遍回收價已下跌一成，以P30 Pro為例，回售價由五千中跌至五千頭左右。他又補充，來放HUAWEI機的顧客也比平日增加了4成之多，「本來HUAWEI機收得好高㗎！但依家個個心裏有條刺，所以咪想及早放機囉！再係咁銷路實有影響，益咗其他牌子，但都有班忠實Fans等緊佢跌價，諗住趁低吸納嘅！」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190522/photo/bkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001_02p.jpg&h=a8f86de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCSL的Trade-in欄中仍找到HUAWEI手機。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190522/photo/bkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001_03p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001_03p.jpg&h=bf8379a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國移動香港的「舊換新」計劃依然有HUAWEI手機在內。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190522/photo/bkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001_04p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001_04p.jpg&h=dbe21469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三禾電氣店長Simon哥指HUAWEI手機的回收價暫時跌了一成。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190522/mobile/bkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190522%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001.html&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSyNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=3d243d83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190522/mobile/bkn-20190522143037089-0522_00982_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6eb3a160e74f2869be4a1bfa050dcd9b52b24fee","tid":1166765,"uid":221819,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"Fake news<br />\n根本就冇人會收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97614a54f459878e5298b8f52845f0e6cff20f3","tid":1166765,"uid":28195,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"舊機P30 Pro 係最後一代可以行Android同上Google Play，應該有得炒喇屌。<br />\n建議Strong Hold唔好放舊版華為機！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3231fb1690fb6b0c8f7a54aef4883da688a7462b","tid":1166765,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"會睇過下新聞的人都唔會再買華為， 買部機攞黎煩咩，又唔係平"},{"pid":"e77a8be6af823d7664ea4d47133a6821604963f3","tid":1166765,"uid":163758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T18:27:46.000Z","msg":"跌剩一成我就信"}]}